{"tid":1846103,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"比煙鏟/想去7仔買口罩嘅溫馨提示","createTime":"2020-01-27T13:05:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-29T18:25:14.000Z","uid":105939,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"2e0ad80793c6fc36ac6e0b3b55c3aff44af9954c","tid":1846103,"uid":105939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T13:05:16.000Z","msg":"7仔間間都冇晒哈密瓜/蜜瓜/赤玉 1號同5號既煙<br />\n因為上面大倉冇貨 所以間間都冇(起碼我返個間同附近幾間至到大角咀個啲都冇)<br />\n你哋要買去OK問下啦<br />\n<br />\n再溫馨提示 5蚊一個口罩大陸做既<br />\n20蚊一包5個口罩台灣做既 (如果仲有貨嘅話,因為我聽到啲客話問咗好多間都冇)<br />\n同埋消毒洗手液都冇(都係啲客話周圍都冇)<br />\n<br />\n順手祝埋大家身體健康<br />\n<br />\n各位知道邊間仲有貨就留低資料比其他手足啦 唔使搵餐死"},{"pid":"6335d9991c47720a20f3544ca97c2838cfb7d9b9","tid":1846103,"uid":144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T13:07:05.000Z","msg":"冇赤玉咪食藍莓囉🚬"},{"pid":"5694876667deb03dfcbf90aa218db215c00f58cf","tid":1846103,"uid":105939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6335d9991c47720a20f3544ca97c2838cfb7d9b9","tid":1846103,"uid":144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T13:07:05.000Z","msg":"冇赤玉咪食藍莓囉🚬"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T13:14:01.000Z","msg":"冇啊啲人黎到聽到話冇 得番8號又係到嘈<br />\n有啲又話剩係要赤玉 問我點算 我最多可以答佢去ok<br />\n費事啲人行餐懵而家講埋"},{"pid":"a63948dddc6fcb3afaa09f8a9025f27bcbe9297c","tid":1846103,"uid":38563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T13:17:31.000Z","msg":"得返一日時間 一句講晒  1.29罷工加黎明行動 做定唔做<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1846030\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1846030</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"83a4aa173764680e43e70740f982ebad10f181b7","tid":1846103,"uid":278089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T13:22:01.000Z","msg":"前排聽到嗰客話食8號煙抗肺炎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4d7e2ff11de57eca1b2db4ba2dcf7cb5ff9dcf2","tid":1846103,"uid":34714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6335d9991c47720a20f3544ca97c2838cfb7d9b9","tid":1846103,"uid":144,"like":0,"dis